         <div type="translation" resp="part:vito">
             <p>Success! Hommage to the Bhagavant, the Buddha! An umbrella: the pious gift of the monk Buddhikaya, together his parents, his sisters Golā and Bodhī, for well-being of the whole world.</p>
         </div>
